        <Meaning id="74b568d7-d501-46c7-b660-6a0efcc5773b" type="Noun">
          <Vi>quê hương, đất nước, tổ quốc</Vi>
          <En>The country or region in which a person was born or has a cultural or ancestral connection.</En>
          <Example>After years abroad, she longed to return to her homeland.</Example>
